{"tid":2435883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國四川與湖北 再爆非洲豬瘟","createTime":"2021-03-06T15:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T02:59:02.000Z","uid":310867,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"abaed4f9da868e446e1dd013664c90bfee9ee971","tid":2435883,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"中國上個月22日大力宣傳，雖受非洲豬瘟影響但是今年下半年豬肉供應有望恢復正常，但中國四川與湖北再度爆發了非洲豬瘟。<br />\n<br />\n中國農業農村部今天（6日）發佈新聞稿，指出四川省阿壩州小金縣、湖北省襄陽市樊城區分別發生1起非洲豬瘟疫情。<br />\n<br />\n四川省的1家養殖場有127頭豬，其中有38頭發病，還有38頭已經死亡；湖北省1輛車違規調運送豬肉的車內也被查出有10頭感染非洲豬瘟。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國農業農村部的新聞稿指出，他們已經針對相關場所、沿途道路及運輸車輛進行徹底清洗消毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3458653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3458653&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=a7e50bb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3458653&h=c3b08c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3458653</a>"},{"pid":"e0a0bac1e78802e91f3ba572dc30ec5e06f85f22","tid":2435883,"uid":78243,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"賤種又想抹黑非洲"},{"pid":"991f9bc01d5951aef949e9591f70fce46597e5ab","tid":2435883,"uid":302117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6487a72f9f1764203aa5b6e42af2a6a89016d0c7","tid":2435883,"uid":52946,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"聯合國:睇唔到中國有豬瘟"},{"pid":"0b509815a11574f7f0c2fd10449ed1785ff5a045","tid":2435883,"uid":3063,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"新型