ws/3458653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3458653&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=a7e50bb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3458653&h=c3b08c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3458653</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好停"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyyXWiu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyyXWiu.png&h=655d3491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國務院農業農村部周二（2日）公布，雲南省文山壯族苗族自治州富寧縣近日查獲一批由外省違規調運的豬隻，並在當中發現非洲豬瘟疫情。該批豬共36隻，並中6隻發病並死亡。同批全部豬隻已被撲殺。<br />\n<br />\n農業農村部周二接獲中國動物疫病預防控制中心報告，指當局在富寧縣廣昆高速富寧指定通道口臨時動物衛生監督檢查站，查獲一車外省違規調運豬隻，經雲南疫控中心確認有非洲豬瘟。<br />\n白粉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送返d連豬比佢地"},{"pid":"7ff74dc1d2376900fc0360ab976b7ecfe7b98526","tid":2435883,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:41:29.000Z","msg":"正視聽，正確學名係中國豬瘟"},{"pid":"1649d54f08ad37a055dc1c9bb95813b09d769e1c","tid":2435883,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"四湖豬瘟"},{"pid":"894ac01b41152b31c06958d7025402dd2c7ba9fc","tid":2435883,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"我中立既 但係叫非洲好似有D歧視喎⋯⋯"},{"pid":"af68748eebf3d21d55a2b9943cbb8956a68b0914","tid":2